        "content": "## Before first run\n- Replace every `REPLACE_WITH_*` value in **Workflow Config**\n- Reconnect **Apify**, **Google Docs**, **Google Sheets**, and **OpenAI** credentials\n- Use a dedicated **private Google Drive folder** for generated resumes\n- Recommended Google scopes: `drive.file`, `documents`, `gmail.send`\n- Keep resume docs private unless you intentionally add a sharing step"
